Date: Fri, 29 May 2026 13:37:03 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 36/73] Probe PDF attach path

The stream wore a wrapper hat,
The helper arrived after that.
It knocked on the frame,
But nobody came,
So now we know where not to bat.
